Description: Nyx - Manage systemd services from the system tray
 Nyx is a Qt-based system tray application that allows you to
 easily manage systemd services from your desktop. Features include:
  * Start, stop, and restart services from the tray
  * Real-time status monitoring with visual indicators
  * Desktop notifications for status changes
  * View systemd logs
  * Support for both user and system services
  * Customizable icons for each service
  * Optional passwordless mode using PolicyKit
